Instructions
1 ‚≠ï‚éÜCkpt to load checkpoint files, then select 1(SD1/XL) 2(XL) or 3(SD3)
2 ‚≠ï‚éÜT5xx / ‚≠ï‚éÜGL nodes must be loaded for SD3. Bypass if using a checkpoint including them.
3 ‚≠ï‚éÜLatent In matching your Stage checkpoints, or load image/latent. Mute unused nodes here.
4 ‚≠ï‚éÜLoadVAE, ensure Stage checkpoint matches, or BYPASS for ckpt with built-in vae. 6/13/24 SD3 built in 
5 ‚≠ïParameters in Selector, Seed, Load ‚ü∑. set default_scale to model scale number and >= scale_factor.
6 ‚≠ïüíæSave filename. Syntax : %nodenameforS&R.widget_value%  Right click node Properties for names. 
7 ‚≠ïI/O disables unused groups. Bypass unused nodes in active groups. Run one Stage at a time on old hardware.
8 ‚≠ïPrompt from +T5X3 and - "Convert Input" on G+ or L+ to write individual prompts per CLIP encoder.
9 queue!
10 enjoy :)

NOTES
- Main menu top cog, Grid size 5, Link render Mode HIDDEN for best appearance. Rewire with links on.
- Collapse nodes before ‚≠ïIO mute/bypass buttons. Nodes crossing groups causes issues.
- To adjust group positions, raise logo window from bottom right corner
- 'Seed' display empties on browser refresh, but 'History' sometimes fills more. üôÉ
- Latents save in /ComfyUI/output/latents/ Change path in ‚≠ïSaveLatent. Copy to /ComfyUI/input to load.
- ‚≠ïLoadLatent or LoadImage takes priority over Empty Latent unless muted. 3 has priority over SD/XL.
- Enable interposer when converting between v1.5/xl/etc. models. No SD3 support yet...
- Each image chimes & notifies browser by default. snake alerts
